	* doc/mpatrol.texi:
	Added more information in NOTES and FAQ.  Changed example 4 for new
	flags.

	* src/info.c: Fixed problem with profiling reallocations.  Oops!

	* src/info.c, src/info.h, src/inter.c:
	Added file and line information to __mp_checkinfo().

