	Added a call to __mp_atexit() to terminate the trace file.

2001-02-21  Graeme Roy  <graeme@epc.co.uk>

	* bin/mupdate: No longer build the documentation archives.

	* build/windows/Makefile, build/windows/NMakefile, build/unix/Makefile,
	  build/unix/Makefile.aix, build/netware/Makefile, build/amiga/Makefile,
	  build/amiga/SMakefile:
