	Added the mptools lint library.

	* doc/Makefile: No longer have a rule to make the documentation archive.

	* doc/README:
	Removed distinction between main distribution and documentation archive.

	* doc/mpatrol.txt, doc/mpatrol.html, doc/mpatrol.info,
	  doc/mpatrol.guide:
	The documentation is now built automatically when a release is made so
	there is no point in having preformatted manual pages in CVS.

	* doc/mpatrol.texi:
	Removed all references to the documentation and manual page archives.
	Added the tools section.

	* doc/texinfo.tex: Updated to the latest version of texinfo.tex.

	* man/Makefile:
	Changed PAGES to CATPAGES.  No longer have a rule to make the manual
	page archive.

	* man/README:
	Removed distinction between main distribution and manual page archive.

	* man/cat3/libmpalloc.3, man/cat3/libmpatrol.3, man/cat1/hexwords.1,
	  man/cat1/mleak.1, man/cat1/mpatrol.1, man/cat1/mpedit.1,
