	Added the __mp_lib* functions to help with autoconf configuration.

	* src/mpatrol.h: Added GNU's mallopt() flags.

	* tests/pass/test2.c, tests/pass/test10.c:
	Changed const to MP_CONST.  Added a new argument to __mp_iterate().

