2001-02-08  Graeme Roy  <graeme@epc.co.uk>

	* man/Makefile: Added the libmpalloc manual page.

	* man/html/libmpalloc.html, man/cat3/libmpalloc.3,
	  man/man3/libmpalloc.3:
	New manual page for the mpalloc library.

