	* man/Makefile:
	Added the mpatrol_man.tar.gz target.  Added the DVI and postscript
	manual pages.

	* man/README: New file describing the manual page formats.

	* man/cat1/mptrace.1, man/man1/mptrace.1: Documented the GUI.

